OL,3,CJohn Swinney sworn in as Scotland's
OL,4,Cfirst minister as new cabinet appointed
OL,6,FMeanwhile, Kate Forbes was declared
OL,7,Fdeputy first minister this afternoon,
OL,8,FITV News Correspondent Peter Smith
OL,9,Freports
OL,11,FJohn Swinney has officially been sworn
OL,12,Fin as Scotland's new first minister at
OL,13,Fthe Court of Session in Edinburgh.
OL,15,FIt comes after the Perthshire North
OL,16,FMSP was on Monday following the
OL,17,Fresignation of Humza Yousaf.
