OL,3,CJohn Swinney sworn in as Scotland's
OL,4,Cfirst minister as new cabinet appointed
OL,6,FMr Swinney, who has previously served
OL,7,Fas finance secretary, education
OL,8,Fsecretary and deputy first minister
OL,9,Ffor the Scottish government, appointed
OL,10,Fhis new cabinet today.
OL,12,FKate Forbes, who was widely touted as
OL,13,Fa successor to Mr Yousaf after a
OL,14,Fdiscussion with the new SNP leader,
OL,15,Fwas declared deputy first minister on
OL,16,Fthis afternoon.
