OL,3,CJohn Swinney sworn in as Scotland's
OL,4,Cfirst minister as new cabinet appointed
OL,6,FShe replaces Shona Robinson, who will
OL,7,Fkeep her other role as finance
OL,8,Fsecretary and will also serve as local
OL,9,Fgovernment secretary. A list seen by
OL,10,FITV News shows all other cabinet
OL,11,Fmembers have remained in the same post.
OL,13,FScotland's most senior judge, the Lord
OL,14,FPresident Lord Carloway, presided over
OL,15,Fthis morning's ceremony, which saw the
OL,16,Fnew leader make his statutory
OL,17,Fdeclaration.
