OL,3,CJohn Swinney sworn in as Scotland's
OL,4,Cfirst minister as new cabinet appointed
OL,6,FMr Swinney raised his right hand and
OL,7,Fbowed his head as Lord Carloway read
OL,8,Fthe three oaths of office ` for the
OL,9,Frole of first minister, the Keeper of
OL,10,Fthe Great Seal and the oath of
OL,11,Fallegiance to the King.
OL,13,FThe Lord President then addressed the
OL,14,Fcourt about the independence of the
OL,15,Fjudiciary.
