OL,3,CJohn Swinney sworn in as Scotland's
OL,4,Cfirst minister as new cabinet appointed
OL,6,FMr Swinney takes on the role at a
OL,7,Fparticularly chaotic time for the SNP,
OL,8,Fwith Mr Yousaf ending his party's
OL,9,Fpowersharing agreement with the
OL,10,FScottish Greens in a row over climate
OL,11,Ftargets and gender reforms.
OL,13,FThe move triggered an expected no
OL,14,Fconfidence vote in Mr Yousaf's
OL,15,Fleadership, but he stood down before
OL,16,Fit could be held. T, but the whole
OL,17,Fsaga has still a reflection of the
OL,18,Flevel of turbulence within the SNP.
