OL,4,Cfirst minister as new cabinet appointed
OL,6,FMeanwhile the husband of former first
OL,7,Fminister Nicola Sturgeon, former SNP
OL,8,Fchief executive Peter Murrell, is
OL,10,FMr Swinney, who was SNP leader between
OL,11,F2000 and 2004, will now have the task
OL,12,Fof restoring unity and calm to
OL,13,FScotland's ruling party.
OL,15,FThe new first minister was accompanied
OL,16,Fby his family, including wife
OL,17,FElizabeth, 13-year-old son Matthew and
OL,18,Fbrother David at today's ceremony.
