OL,3,CJohn Swinney sworn in as Scotland's
OL,4,Cfirst minister as new cabinet appointed
OL,6,FAfter winning the support of MSPs in
OL,7,FHolyrood on Tuesday, Mr Swinney
OL,8,Fpledged to devote himself to the job
OL,9,Fafter being chosen to become the
OL,10,Fseventh person to be first minister
OL,11,Fsince the Scottish Parliament was
OL,12,Festablished 25 years ago.JMr Swinney
OL,13,Fsaid it was an "extraordinary
OL,14,Fprivilege" to become Scotland's new
OL,15,Ffirst minister as he pledged to "give
OL,16,Feverything I have" to the role.
